11 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
12 An Act relating to legislative referendums; directing
special election on proposed amendments to the
13 Constitution and state statutes be held; specifying
certain date; referencing House Bill No. 4440 of the
14 60th Oklahoma Legislature; referencing House Joint
Resolution No. 1024 of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature;
15 directing filing; and declaring an emergency.
16
17
18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
20 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
21 Pursuant to Section 3 of Article V of the Oklahoma Constitution,
22 a special election is hereby ordered to be held throughout the State
23 of Oklahoma on Tuesday, August 25, 2026, at which time the proposed
24 referendums, as set forth in Enrolled House Bill No. 4440 of the 2nd
HB4063 HFLR Page 1
